<figureCitation id="D177C08579F2046A2C223B2D83A444BE" captionStart="Figures 13–18" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 13 - 18. 13 Bilyaxia (Tomasia) maculicollis (Kerremans, 1887), female, 4.6 mm (Argentina, Entre Rios) 14 Bilyaxia (Tomasia) lata (Kerremans, 1903), male, 5.0 mm (Brasil, Rio Grande do Sul) 15 Bilyaxia (Tomasia) cinctipennis (Kerremans, 1913), male holotype, 7.0 mm 16 Brasilaxia costifera (Obenberger, 1913), male, 6.3 mm (Brasil, Curityba) 17 Paracuris bimaculata bimaculata (Gory, 1841), male, 7.1 mm (Argentina, Catamarca) 18 the same, female, 7.2 mm (Brasil, Bermejo)." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/21690" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Figs 17, 18</figureCitation>
