<subSubSection id="AEFCBDFBDBCFB3813B78D91A66C4794A" lastPageId="25" lastPageNumber="42" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" type="type species">
<paragraph id="4C8225E0F4CAF1ABB432B6E93D32E67C" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Type species.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="10811A0E97582A38F38C6F5BCB28A3EE" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">
<taxonomicName id="3C56E296E5BDE89A5B8F8314683DB1FB" authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1872" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Curis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hemiptera">
<emphasis id="4ECDE821D004215D1E3A73A4968D1517" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Curis hemiptera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Burmeister, 1872 by original designation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="47AD3B24AA73F39C3C23C36C864AEF97" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">
<pageBreakToken id="7DCF95E33DC5F94FB887DFEAE300D321" pageId="25" pageNumber="42" start="start">This</pageBreakToken>
monotypic genus lacks taxonomic problems and has very often been treated as a subgenus of 
<taxonomicName id="8A95E469804B23C7FE4EEE89DDF92B0D" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="42" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="5ED6B41019D065DC74DA709E56E428B2" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">Anthaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, e.g. 
<bibRefCitation id="F942DE7A24846B7887FCA496BAFEA772" author="Bellamy, CL" journalOrPublisher="Navorsinge van die nasionale Museum, Bloemfontein," pageId="26" pageNumber="43" pagination="405 - 472" refId="B1" refString="Bellamy, CL, 1985. A catalogue of the higher taxa of the family Buprestidae (Coleoptera). Navorsinge van die nasionale Museum, Bloemfontein, 4 (15): 405 - 472" title="A catalogue of the higher taxa of the family Buprestidae (Coleoptera)." volume="4" year="1985">Bellamy (1985</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="08AA4D5B3CF919CF4481607455844DC3" author="Bellamy, CL" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="1 - 197" refId="B2" refString="Bellamy, CL, 2003. An illustrated summary of the higher classification of the superfamily Buprestoidea (Coleoptera). Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum 10: 1 - 197" title="An illustrated summary of the higher classification of the superfamily Buprestoidea (Coleoptera)." volume="10" year="2003">2003</bibRefCitation>
), 
<bibRefCitation id="829A95B2FD8FC796DA4D21D9A1F7EA76" author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="3 - 190" refId="B9" refString="Bily, S, 1997. World catalogue of the genus Anthaxia Eschscholtz, 1829 (Coleopreta, Buprestidae). Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum 2: 3 - 190" title="World catalogue of the genus Anthaxia Eschscholtz, 1829 (Coleopreta, Buprestidae)." volume="2" year="1997">
<normalizedToken id="829C8B10B28E33DD107B5B0BAB9D510B" originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
(1997)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="E57651F5D9A77CFD98B0A9C3E503BD01" author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria)" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="103 - 165" refId="B19" refString="Cobos, A, 1956. Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria) 5: 103 - 165" title="Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb." volume="5" year="1956">Cobos (1956</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="A425974BD39C655D03E996AEADF3FACA" author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Revista Brasileira de Biologia," pageId="28" pageNumber="45" pagination="707 - 709" refId="B23" refString="Cobos, A, 1986. Opuscula buprestologica II - Nueva especie y nuevo sexo de Anthaxia de Mejico. Revista Brasileira de Biologia, 46: 707 - 709" title="Opuscula buprestologica II - Nueva especie y nuevo sexo de Anthaxia de Mejico." volume="46" year="1986">1986</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="C6D5547C8D5C58F706DEADDDF5EFD3C4" author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="1 - 11" refId="B12" refString="Bily, S, 2004. Taxonomic studies on Anthaxiina Gory &amp; Laporte de Castelnau and Curina Holynski (Coleoptera: Buprestidae). Zootaxa 555: 1 - 11" title="Taxonomic studies on Anthaxiina Gory &amp; Laporte de Castelnau and Curina Holynski (Coleoptera: Buprestidae)." volume="555" year="2004">
<normalizedToken id="8A107FCD44D37E8B8EBFE9EEEF08E344" originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
(2004)
</bibRefCitation>
upgraded it to genus which was was accepted by 
<bibRefCitation id="523603D6C4346B7F99420D2F6C3AFB49" author="Bellamy, CL" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" refId="B3" refString="Bellamy, CL, 2008. A world catalogue and bibliography of the jewel beetles (Coleoptera: Buprestoidea). Volume 3. Buprestinae: Pterobothrini through Agrilinae: Rhaeboscelina. Pensoft series faunistica No. 78, Sofia - Moscow, pp. (1-2) + 1261-1932." title="A world catalogue and bibliography of the jewel beetles (Coleoptera: Buprestoidea). Volume 3. Buprestinae: Pterobothrini through Agrilinae: Rhaeboscelina. Pensoft series faunistica No. 78, Sofia - Moscow, pp. (1 - 2) + 1261 - 1932." year="2008">Bellamy (2008)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1F2C77F65FF5EF82F13A441C19CFCCD2" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">
The type species, 
<taxonomicName id="AD80158D9F6EF36C101D79701015D168" authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1872" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Curis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="42" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hemiptera">
<emphasis id="5924C2D34416881A67DEBDCDB105A19D" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">Curis hemiptera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, was synonymized with 
<taxonomicName id="72919CB07BD18F4BB354B3EA38DA3CEE" authorityName="Gory" authorityYear="1841" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="42" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bimaculata">
<emphasis id="52C6FECB8DB231E99FDAC943B7AA25CE" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">Anthaxia bimaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Gory, 1841 by 
<bibRefCitation id="2D6A2EB1E6CDDBCBA32E9F08E82B7564" author="Berg, FGC" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" refId="B4" refString="Berg, FGC, 1884. Communicatios. [Notes synonymiques.] Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France (6) 4, Bulletin: CXXX- CXXXI." title="Communicatios. [Notes synonymiques.] Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France (6) 4, Bulletin: CXXX- CXXXI." year="1884">Berg (1884)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="63FCF2E0BAC7D50B1DA21D46758582C5" author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria)" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="103 - 165" refId="B19" refString="Cobos, A, 1956. Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria) 5: 103 - 165" title="Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb." volume="5" year="1956">Cobos (1956)</bibRefCitation>
described the subspecies 
<taxonomicName id="665BA837B3CF73551395F963B84D632E" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="42" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="bimaculata" subGenus="Paracuris" subSpecies="litigiosa">
<emphasis id="AD5E6163CE3F57A073BB15286330B71F" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">Anthaxia (Paracuris) bimaculata litigiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Cobos, 1956 from Argentina (Rio Colorado, Rio Negro).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="91EFC07062DFE574F917769BB5596C48" pageId="25" pageNumber="42" type="note">
<paragraph id="576E959D0618CDC5F68FCDB0C3A95C39" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="46F97F029490AC0597230D0B5301BC87" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">
The nominotypical subspecies possesses rather strong sexual dichromatism (
<figureCitation id="3148B9B9B8FFD4FD051C7E8EDA9E83D4" captionStart="Figures 13–18" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 13 - 18. 13 Bilyaxia (Tomasia) maculicollis (Kerremans, 1887), female, 4.6 mm (Argentina, Entre Rios) 14 Bilyaxia (Tomasia) lata (Kerremans, 1903), male, 5.0 mm (Brasil, Rio Grande do Sul) 15 Bilyaxia (Tomasia) cinctipennis (Kerremans, 1913), male holotype, 7.0 mm 16 Brasilaxia costifera (Obenberger, 1913), male, 6.3 mm (Brasil, Curityba) 17 Paracuris bimaculata bimaculata (Gory, 1841), male, 7.1 mm (Argentina, Catamarca) 18 the same, female, 7.2 mm (Brasil, Bermejo)." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/21690" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">Figs 17, 18</figureCitation>
). The female is rather similar to 
<taxonomicName id="8F7E698CB8303B7C9990C7A362ED37E6" baseAuthorityName="Cobos" baseAuthorityYear="1956" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Paracuris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="42" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="bimaculata" subSpecies="litigiosa">
<emphasis id="4BEDAA0DF06E9797CE5CEB11BD5EB961" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">Paracuris bimaculata litigiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and only the different form of the male genitalia (Figs 45-48 in 
<bibRefCitation id="B96A8EA31922DC22DEFBFBE17204A63A" author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria)" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="103 - 165" refId="B19" refString="Cobos, A, 1956. Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria) 5: 103 - 165" title="Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb." volume="5" year="1956">Cobos, 1956</bibRefCitation>
) justifies treating the subspecies 
<emphasis id="1F5729C9DC6FE45C7FDCB427BA335182" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="42">litigiosa</emphasis>
as a valid taxon.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
